Package frc.robot.io.implementations.motor

Class MotorIOElevatorStub

java.lang.Object
frc.robot.io.implementations.motor.MotorIOBase
frc.robot.io.implementations.motor.MotorIOElevatorStub
All Implemented Interfaces:
MotorIO
public class MotorIOElevatorStub extends MotorIOBase
A "Stub" implementation of a MotorIO that can be used for initial software bring-up/testing in simulation. Simulates the physics of an Elevator connected via a rope/pulley to translated rotational motion to linear motion.
